Paper: hep-th/9711064

Date: 1997-11-10

Title: Effective actions, relative cohomology and Chern Simons forms

Authors: J. A. de Azcarraga, A. J. Macfarlane and J. C. Perez Bueno

Comments: 11 pages. Latex2e file. Published version

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B419 (1998) 186-194

The explicit expression of all the WZW effective actions for a simple group Gbroken down to a subgroup H is established in a simple and direct way, and theformal similarity of these actions to the Chern-Simons forms is explained.Applications are also discussed.